readLater.title: Covid-19 Live Updates: Kelly Loeffler Isolating After Test Results - The New York Times
readLater.author: Katie Thomas, Noah Weiland
readLater.description: New York City and New York State differ on how they measure the crucial threshold of 3 percent positivity. Unlike the rest of the U.S., Hawaii has seen a decline in infections. South Korea and Japan face surges.

readLater.title: Guitar Center is filing for bankruptcy - CNN
readLater.author: Alexis Benveniste, CNN Business
readLater.description: Guitar Center is filing for Chapter 11 bankruptcy, the latest company to go bankrupt during the pandemic that has decimated America's retail sector.
